snippet.title: ZYNET Release Trailer
snippet.description:
ZYNET is a fun and original retro sci-fi action VR game that redefines what VR gameplay can be. Toss, swipe, punch, take control, dodge, and think your way through a mysterious and dangerous alternate dimension.

Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1246170/ZYNET/

Join the conversation on Discord: https://discord.gg/Q9ZsRUR

Follow @ZYNETVR on twitter: https://twitter.com/zynetvr

#indiedev #virtualreality #gametrailer #vr #gamedev #indiegame #madewithunity
